{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "第五回“大婉”主要讲述了马如龙在破庙中被点穴后，与神秘女子大婉的互动。大婉长相丑陋但武功高强，性格古怪直率。她拿走了马如龙的皮裘和白马，却在关键时刻救了他一命。彭天霸被神秘人杀死，马如龙发现阴谋远比想象中复杂。大婉最终在酒楼请马如龙吃饭喝酒，并透露了自己的名字。本章通过两人的对话，展现了大婉的聪明狡猾和马如龙的无奈善良。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "想不到那胖子居然走了，想不到你居然还活着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_null",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "幸好马如龙还能说话，忍不住道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这不是你的，现在已经不是你的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为你已经把它送给了那胖子，那胖子又送给了我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "所以现在这件衣服已经是我的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "又忍不住",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你能不能加点火？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "加火干什么？我又不冷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你不冷，我冷。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我不冷，你为什么会冷？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "年轻人一定要能够吃苦耐劳，冷一点又有什么关系？你年纪轻轻，连这点苦都不能吃，将来还能做什么大事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "不知道天是不是快亮了，我出去看看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "外面……外面有个人。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "就是刚才那个胖子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他还没有走？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "还没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他在外面干什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "谁知道他在干什么？他一个人躺在那里，好像睡着了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你一定看错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_null",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "她的眼睛实在长得不难看，至少比老鼠要好看一点。马如龙说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你自己为什么不出去看看？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我明白了，你一定也跟我一样，也被那胖子踢了一脚，所以现在连动都不能动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_null",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可是她刚走出去，又大叫一声，跑了回来，看样子比刚才还吃惊。马如龙道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他……他还在，他永远都走不了的。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为他已经死了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他真的死了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "绝对死了，从头到脚都死了，死得干干净净。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你看不看得出他是怎么会忽然死了的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我当然看得出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_null",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这个人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "什么事不行？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我们绝不能够再留在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我是个女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "英雄好汉都是男人，君子也一定是男人，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "所以怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "所以我既不是君子，也不是英雄好汉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "好，你走吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可是我走不动，我一定要把你的马骑走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "好，你骑走吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你这个人实在是个好人，只可惜……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "只可惜什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "只可惜好人都是不长命的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "路人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "有个死人在这里，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "路人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "还有没有救？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_null",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "一刀致命，神仙也救不活。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_null",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "那一定是天马堂的白龙驹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_null",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "一刀致命，杀了就走，好辣的手，好狠的人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_null",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他逃不了的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_null",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可是彭天霸……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "彭天霸会在这里等，马如龙却不会等，我们追！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "上来，快上来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他只有苦笑，",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_null",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "马如龙只有坐下。她又大声道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "年轻人不但要能饿，还要能吃，你不把这碗炖羊肉吃完，不管你想说什么，我都不理你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_null",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "吃饱了肚子，就可以喝酒了，快喝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "不喝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你是不是要我捏着你的鼻子灌下去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_null",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这样才像话，一个人，如果连酒都不敢喝，算什么男子汉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_null",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可是你放心，这酒里没有毒，我并不想毒死你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "现在我是不是已经可以说话了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "有话快说，有屁快放。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你怎么会跑到这里来了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我高兴来，就来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你本来明明是往东边去的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可是我忽然想到西边来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你不是在盯着我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你是不是以为你自己长得很漂亮，女人都要盯着你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_null",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "马如龙动容道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你怎么会知道的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你是不是看见了冯超凡和绝和尚，是不是他们告诉你的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你喝酒是不是一定要用大碗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你为什么一定要用大碗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "只有小婉喝酒才用小碗，我又不是小婉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你也知道小婉？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你问得太多了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可是你连一句都没有回答。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "那只因为你问的都是不该问的话，该问的你都没有问。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我该问什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你吃了我的肉，喝了我的酒，至少应该先问问我贵姓大名的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你贵姓大名？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "小婉喝酒用小碗，我用大碗喝酒，应该叫什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你叫大婉？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那女人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这次你总算变得聪明些了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    }
